/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eWhat is the prize?:\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eAs of now,\r\n27,000 credits, but it will probably be 30,000 by the end because I’ll have the\r\ncredits to provide that.\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eWhat is an Adventure map?\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eAn adventure\r\nmap is a map built in Vanilla minecraft, usually using command blocks, to\r\ncreate a mini map that another player can download and try to beat, like a\r\ndungeon for example, you can use parkour, custom mobs, puzzles, for each\r\nlevel.\u0026nbsp; You usually are on \u003ca href=\"http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Adventure\"\u003eadventure mode\u003c/a\u003e when you\r\nplay these maps.\u0026nbsp; If you still do not\r\nquite understand, here are some \u003ca href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzodacNT0eiTODX0BASvHzSuP15sH-3wE\"\u003egameplays\u003c/a\u003e\r\nof adventure maps.\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eHow do I submit my map?\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eJust post it\r\nbelow! Make it look like it’s your own thread if you’d like, just make sure to\r\nprovide a download link and a brief description of the game you created!\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eHow is a winner determined?\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eI will play\r\neach game; I will record each one and post it on my \u003ca href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZgF8f3uT2BN5qPOVcsTjkQ\"\u003eYoutube channel\u003c/a\u003e.\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003eOnce the deadline\r\nhas been met, I will score each map submitted like so:\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003e1-5 points\r\nfor aesthetics, who doesn’t like a nice looking map?\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003e1-5 points\r\nfor storyline, an intriguing story can make the map all the better\u003co:p\u003e\u003c/o:p\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:\u0026quot;Arial\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;sans-serif\u0026quot;\"\u003e1-10 points\r\nfor gameplay, this one is special because this is more important than\r\naesthetics and storyline. How smoothly th